text:
oo bhosdike,
Bhai pahele yad dilata na ki aj last date hai isko likhne ka. Kya kya likhu bhai. Sab kuch toh nai likh sakta is memoir mai. 

Day 1 hostel mai, sab aise hi zada nai bol rahe aur ek tu... usi din se bakchodi shuru. aur us din se abhi tak level upar hi gaya hai bas. Tu proper depiction hai dilli ka launde ka. 

Phir toh kya hi tha, 4 sal aise hi khatam hue hai tere room aur uncle ji k room mai bhate bhate. Chaye woh 1st year wala bluff ka game ho ya last year wali kissi ki bitching.

Pure campus mai kya chal raha hai, kya raaz hai kaunsi bat kaise bat, sab ka khabar tere pas hai- chaye woh hall 3 ki bedsheet ki kahani ho ya kissi ka laptop chori (xDD). 

Bhai woh "Gupta Rice company" aur "kauua k ghosle mai humara koyal" ne kya bhosda kiya. Is idea ne maaza hi dila diya tha. Sala abhi tak hassi ati hai. 

"bhai lag gayi" iske bad jo khushi hui â¤ï¸â¤ï¸. Party toh pahele bhi chal rahi thi, lekin iske bad toh aur khushi k saath hui. XD. Lekin jald hi wapis jana pada. Jo bhi hai- woh kuch din ache se yad rahega- quarantine ho ya normal hall 12 ki zindagi.

Waise tu news anchor mat banna, debates mai samne wale ko kuch bolne hi nai dega. ğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚

Bhai itna kabhi nai hasa honga, jitna tere saath hasa hu. (bc itna gussa bhi kissi ne nai dilaya)
Jo bhi hua maaza aya... tere bina yeh Priank nai hota. 

Khush reh, aur tension kam liya kar, aur please bandi ki choices achi kar le.
Trip p chalo BCCC.
